Class TarArchiveOutputEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xbib.io.archive.tar.TarArchiveOutputEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArchiveEntry, TarConstants

    public class TarArchiveOutputEntry
extends Object
implements TarConstants, ArchiveEntry
    This class represents an entry in a Tar archive for output
